        "subject": "=Renewal proposal for {{ $json.deal_name }} — 60 days to go",
        "emailType": "text",
        "message": "=Hi,\n\nI wanted to reach out as the contract for {{ $json.deal_name }} is coming up for renewal in {{ $json.days_left }} days.\n\nI'd love to put together a renewal proposal that works for you. Could we schedule a 30-minute call this week to discuss your needs going forward?\n\nContract value: £{{ $json.amount }} | Expiry: {{ $json.contract_end_date }}\n\nLooking forward to continuing our partnership.\n\nBest,\nAccount Management",
