    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 17 — Contract Renewal Pipeline\n\n**HubSpot setup required:**\n1. Custom deal property: contract_end_date (date)\n2. Custom deal properties (boolean): renewal_email_90d_sent, renewal_email_60d_sent, renewal_email_30d_sent\n\n**Email routing:** Currently sends to RENEWAL_TEST_EMAIL env variable. Update each Gmail node's 'Send To' field to use the actual contact email from the associated HubSpot contact.\n\n**To get contact email:** Add a HubSpot 'Get Contact' node between 'Route by Tier' and the Gmail nodes, using the deal's associated contact ID.",
        "height": 708,
        "width": 1716
      },
